892
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:25,320
Happy birthday, sweetheart.

893
00:43:25,440 --> 00:43:27,200
- Ta.
- Roxanne.

894
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:28,360
Happy birthday.

895
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:29,640
Happy birthday.

