- Face up to what?

985
00:49:25,960 --> 00:49:28,800
[Monica] She's left her card.

986
00:49:30,000 --> 00:49:32,880
Oh, well. I'll post it
on to her.

987
00:49:33,000 --> 00:49:34,880
[Cynthia] I'll take it.

988
00:49:35,000 --> 00:49:37,880
